{"tid":2238392,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有情緒病真係好辛苦","createTime":"2020-10-11T05:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T12:29:29.000Z","uid":63720,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"46cbe852b0d89b6eb8df297d20c5f7178dc3855f","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"個人有情緒病<br />\n我都好想否認，但事實上真係有病<br />\n個病好似話嚟就嚟咁<br />\n每日都過得好辛苦<br />\n食到既，但只係為左生存所以先食<br />\n訓教要靠藥物先訓到<br />\n每日心情都好低落<br />\n心入面好唔舒服<br />\n好似冇野令你開心返<br />\n平時鐘意做既野都冇動力、冇心情去做<br />\n淨係想訓同訓<br />\n覺得人生好無意義<br />\n諗唔到令我開心既事<br />\n個個都叫我諗開d<br />\n其實我都想，但我真係控制唔到自己既負面諗法<br />\n而且經常會有想死既諗法<br />\n覺得個世界好灰暗 <br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1294cf8abb17df4628979666cee58af36415dded","tid":2238392,"uid":256786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"我明"},{"pid":"512b046647e8c90b7b0a625e7d09ac789c25d68b","tid":2238392,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"情緒病只係一時<br />\n好返就會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460222cad42307505ac631f018c3fee1009b6cf0","tid":2238392,"uid":324681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"以前拍拖試過，反而單身後立即痊癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81674685e237948799d733206594da102e304ae9","tid":2238392,"uid":357658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed5eb67fb2a351febbacf38f2de072c5cf6021e","tid":2238392,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"其實係因為咩事導致有情緒病"},{"pid":"c47b7609134342dd46acc019aa1457d1af5c0fe5","tid":2238392,"uid":345392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"真係唔係我開嘅咩呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f239dbf7d141ad400734ebd2ead09bff425f45","tid":2238392,"uid":366245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afd59fbb64d4eb0949357a9966847cb551727469","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed5eb67fb2a351febbacf38f2de072c5cf6021e","tid":2238392,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"其實係因為咩事導致有情緒病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"每方面都有<br />\n工作、家庭等等<br />\n只係自己一直積埋積埋咁<br />\n唔知自己原來咁大問題<br />\n跟住無啦啦就大爆發"},{"pid":"884b3ca4c5cb5c2f53ccaeb2fda4b652a1d3daf1","tid":2238392,"uid":262886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46cbe852b0d89b6eb8df297d20c5f7178dc3855f","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"個人有情緒病<br />\n我都好想否認，但事實上真係有病<br />\n個病好似話嚟就嚟咁<br />\n每日都過得好辛苦<br />\n食到既，但只係為左生存所以先食<br />\n訓教要靠藥物先訓到<br />\n每日心情都好低落<br />\n心入面好唔舒服<br />\n好似冇野令你開心返<br />\n平時鐘意做既野都冇動力、冇心情去做<br />\n淨係想訓同訓<br />\n覺得人生好無意義<br />\n諗唔到令我開心既事<br />\n個個都叫我諗開d<br />\n其實我都想，但我真係控制唔到自己既負面諗法<br />\n而且經常會有想死既諗法<br />\n覺得個世界好灰暗 <br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8559d47242ce8a46f18c97f1f8d9b1d565dc732d","tid":2238392,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"沖個<strong>熱</strong>水涼<br />\n<br />\n淋透個身 訓前食少少野 保持空氣流通 開住佢訓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ht9GJ8PeVeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fht9GJ8PeVeM&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=5f388dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ht9GJ8PeVeM</a>"},{"pid":"ca284ebe074fd19115b2c1f8ec39360bf4acde5d","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"884b3ca4c5cb5c2f53ccaeb2fda4b652a1d3daf1","tid":2238392,"uid":262886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46cbe852b0d89b6eb8df297d20c5f7178dc3855f","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"個人有情緒病<br />\n我都好想否認，但事實上真係有病<br />\n個病好似話嚟就嚟咁<br />\n每日都過得好辛苦<br />\n食到既，但只係為左生存所以先食<br />\n訓教要靠藥物先訓到<br />\n每日心情都好低落<br />\n心入面好唔舒服<br />\n好似冇野令你開心返<br />\n平時鐘意做既野都冇動力、冇心情去做<br />\n淨係想訓同訓<br />\n覺得人生好無意義<br />\n諗唔到令我開心既事<br />\n個個都叫我諗開d<br />\n其實我都想，但我真係控制唔到自己既負面諗法<br />\n而且經常會有想死既諗法<br />\n覺得個世界好灰暗 <br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直係人地面前好堅強咁<br />\n宜家自己有問題<br />\n都有同人講<br />\n但我個心其實唔想成日揾人傾<br />\n因為覺得自己好煩 <br />\n好驚會麻煩到人<br />\n我食藥 食完藥訓醒都係同一個感覺<br />\n心情都係極低落<br />\n好辛苦 好想結束咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6baf3e32913b26245e040475b081cfbadc14e5","tid":2238392,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca284ebe074fd19115b2c1f8ec39360bf4acde5d","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"884b3ca4c5cb5c2f53ccaeb2fda4b652a1d3daf1","tid":2238392,"uid":262886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46cbe852b0d89b6eb8df297d20c5f7178dc3855f","tid":2238392,"uid":63720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"個人有情緒病<br />\n我都好想否認，但事實上真係有病<br />\n個病好似話嚟就嚟咁<br />\n每日都過得好辛苦<br />\n食到既，但只係為左生存所以先食<br />\n訓教要靠藥物先訓到<br />\n每日心情都好低落<br />\n心入面好唔舒服<br />\n好似冇野令你開心返<br />\n平時鐘意做既野都冇動力、冇心情去做<br />\n淨係想訓同訓<br />\n覺得人生好無意義<br />\n